Next release
------------------------------------------
Version : 2.1.0
Due : ????-??-??

- cleanup demo building and installation
- bring improved code in showaccel demo to showaccel2 demo
* why is directfb drawing on only every other pixel column? (was DFB bug)
* use config file instead of static accel_strings array in fbdev
* enable DirectFB
- KGI-target (compiling framework, probably only working with Matrox Cards)
- make Xlib a helper target for X
- Make XF86DGA working with XF86 3.x and XF86 4.x
- improve modelist.inc
- documentate tele-target in libggi/doc/targets.txt
- add display-auto to separate OS dependent auto-detect routines from
  libggi core
- remove pre-gii typedefs from <ggi/types.h>


